//Use an images pixel array to apply a custom filter to it. For example, take an image that is in color and display it in black and white. Or take a black and white image and display it with color. Or try something different! Look for inspiration from, but do not use the p5.Image filter( ) method nor tint( ). (Source:HappyCoding.io)

